Dear Javier,

The package has been updated and should work for you fine now. Note that function mcp.fnc does not return the fourth plot (dffits) anymore. We still have to figure out a way to compute the dffits for the new merMod objects.

Also note that mcposthoc.fnc doesn't work with pvals.fnc / MCMC anymore.
Please see Note in help page.

Finally, the package gained function plotLMER.fnc from archived package languageR. It's the same, except for the bits related to mcmc.

Please let me know if you encounter other problems.

Sincerely,







